{"tid":128502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[智能化管理] 告密APP 北京上線","createTime":"2017-02-21T01:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T03:19:08.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8c4ebe825919a3aaaeacab1b5b7d6622bc851e","tid":128502,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T01:02:10.000Z","msg":"北京「朝陽群眾」 告密APP上線遭轟 <br />\n更新時間：2017-02-19 20:51:39 <br />\n<br />\n【新唐人亞太台 2017 年 02 月 19 日訊】日前，北京警方發佈了一款名為「朝陽群眾HD」的手機應用程式(APP)，其主要的作用是「舉報你附近的人」。分析認為，如果一個政權需要依靠民眾告密來統治，社會將越來越墮落。 <br />\n<br />\n北京市朝陽公安局官方微博13號介紹：由朝陽警方和相關單位研發的「朝陽群眾HD」APP系統，已上線測試。 <br />\n<br />\n該款 App在蘋果 App Store中的應用描述：這是一個集成警民合作，案件下發、群眾上傳的平臺。警方的口號是：「下載這款App，做朝陽群眾，舉報你附近的人」 <br />\n<br />\n旅美原大陸歷史學教授 劉因全：「中共在文革的時候，這種告密文化達到了登峰造極的地步，甚至夫妻反目，父子成仇，這種事都有很多，中共一貫就是這樣做，是挑動群眾鬥群眾的高手。」 <br />\n<br />\n其實，除了「朝陽群眾」APP，中共已有多種舉報平臺，甚至還會祭出所謂的「在線紅包鼓勵」。 <br />\n<br />\n自由撰稿人 朱欣欣：「中共善於搞什麼所謂的人民戰爭，搞這一套，而不是把法律的問題由司法部門去解決，實際上這樣完全沒有司法獨立，讓整個群眾圍著政治權力行動，而不是尊重人們自由的選擇，等於說逼迫老百姓參與權力治理的系統之中，完全忽視或無視民間社會自由的選擇，這個是很無恥的。」 <br />\n<br />\n自由撰稿人朱欣欣認為，那些主動做「朝陽群眾」去舉報別人的人，絕對是被中共黨文化洗腦的一個結果，也擔心中共的情報網會因此無限延伸。 <br />\n<br />\n[url]link:<a href=\"http://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20170219/video/190656.html[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com.tw%2Fb5%2F20170219%2Fvideo%2F190656.html%5B%2Furl%5D&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=3ae83e11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20170219/video/190656.html[/url]</a>"},{"pid":"63d569493706166caa910d23cdd87c80481e1ab0","tid":128502,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T02:00:37.000Z","msg":"支那推出告密App，方便市民篤人背脊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/127086/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/127086/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57aadd091de8f087d13921da0e6527d606a39909","tid":128502,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T02:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那推出告密App，方便市民篤人背脊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/127086/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/127086/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n這個POST 討論 如何利 智能化技術 對抗共匪"},{"pid":"b70170801519cc59b8b13f92b993493b2f09d78d","tid":128502,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T02:07:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支那推出告密App，方便市民篤人背脊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/127086/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/127086/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n這個POST 討論 如何利用 智能化技術 對抗共匪</blockquote>"},{"pid":"51e9180f40fc53bd5a7ffd7d11442e6268a952d1","tid":128502,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T02:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等緊報串果d俾人捉返轉頭"},{"pid":"9f59a265bac7c2ce5021604c91eaab636a008a51","tid":128502,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T02:19:23.000Z","msg":"香港用唔用得，我想篤林鄭、689、李私煙...不能盡錄"},{"pid":"7023162876df80c19dcd054329345255cdc82a7f","tid":128502,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T02:19:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等緊報串果d俾人捉返轉頭</blockquote><br />\n大家入去，面對面咁，不打不相識。"},{"pid":"f585c6c3c7030057fd8e5124cb90fb163fe806b8","tid":128502,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T02:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a1c27c2fc7b4a7a46b43d7f240dc6ff5612109","tid":128502,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20